ut it for a long time after you have watched it. there are many references to other sources and some peculiar choices like blank eyes for example. there is a deep message going on in this, and it is up to you to find your own meaning from it. it is a true work of art. It is filmed in black and white, and has a brilliant score. it starts off very upbeat and then towards the end gets melancholy. This is a must see, an incredible film!","date":"2005-03-19","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/27/8a/137219_N0Ok2.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/27/8a/137219_N0Ok2.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/27/8a/137219_N0Ok2.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/27/8a/137219_N0Ok2.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/27/8a/137219_N0Ok2.jpg"},"rating":{"rank":0,"total":3,"score":6,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":0,"5":1,"6":1,"7":1,"8":0,"9":0,"10":0}},"tags":[{"name":"短片","count":3},{"name":"2005","count":1},{"name":"欧美","count":1}],"eps":1,"collection":{"wish":6,"collect":10,"doing":0,"on_hold":1,"dropped":4}},{"id":324777,"type":2,"name":"EREMENTAR GERAD-蒼空の戦旗-","name_cn":"EREMENTAR GERAD-苍空的战旗-","summary":"","date":"2005-03-19","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/c8/a0/324777_9zjCu.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/c8/a0/324777_9zjCu.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/c8/a0/324777_9zjCu.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/c8/a0/324777_9zjCu.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/c8/a0/324777_9zjCu.jpg"},"rating":{"rank":0,"total":2,"score":5,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":1,"5":0,"6":1,"7":0,"8":0,"9":0,"10":0}},"tags":[{"name":"2005","count":2},{"name":"奇幻","count":1},{"name":"空","count":1}],"eps":0,"collection":{"wish":6,"collect":4,"doing":0,"on_hold":0,"dropped":2}},{"id":324778,"type":2,"name":"R²[rise R to the second power]","name_cn":"","summary":"","date":"2005-03-19","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200